title: 🌇Walk to Anything Eastside or Downtown
posting_body: ['😃 Gorgeous contemporary 1 bed.', 'Walk out your door and be surrounded with things to do.', 'Easy access to grocery.', "Great if you don't have a car!", '😃 Community offers rooftop deck with downtown views, Large pool with great sunlight at all hours, nice gym, garage parking with gated access.', 'This spot is in a great location!', '😃 Apartment offers nice balcony!', "Text for more info or a tour and we'll get you set!", 'Moving from out of town?', 'No problem, let me know', 'and I can get videos of the units/property myself to be sent over to you.', "🙌 Is this close to what you're looking for, but not quite it?", 'Shoot me a message and we can get going on a search that matches your needs!', "I'm here to get you a great deal at great properties.", '🙌', 'Taylor Boykin', 'Phone:', 'show contact info', 'Craft Apartment Locators', 'My service is 100% FREE for you!', '*Pricing and lease terms subject to change by the property.', 'Pictures are taken from the property but may not be exact unit.', 'No worries!', 'I can get you all the detailed info over to you.*', '😃Serving all Austin areas: North Austin / South Austin / Central Austin / East Austin | SoLa | South Congress | Lady Bird Lake | Downtown | Travis Heights | Central | Barton | Lamar | Clarksville | Crestview | Zilker | Domain | SoCo | South Central | Oak Hill | Bee Cave | Lake Travis | Southpark Meadows | Arboretum | 78704 | 78703 | 78702 | 78701 | 78745']
